						<summary>

						<p>Below the Jaina figure at Pēchchi-paḷḷam, on the Ummaṇāmalai hill.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Undated. In <hi rend="italic">Vaṭṭeḻuttu</hi> characters. (8th cent. A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Records that the image was carved on behalf of Vēḷaṉ Chaḍaivaṉ, a shepherd of Pārūr in Miḻalai-kūṟṟam, by Chaḍaiyappaṉ of Nā[ṉ]kūṟ in Pāṇāḍu.</p>						

